OL,5,Clives'
OL,7,FHawick residents say proposals to
OL,8,Fdowngrade the town's fire station
OL,9,Fcould 'cost lives'.
OL,11,FThe Scottish Fire and Rescue Service
OL,12,Fhave opened a 12-week national public
OL,13,Fconsultation to hear views on their
OL,14,Fproposals to change the way the
OL,15,Fservice operates.
OL,17,FHawick Fire Station could be
OL,18,Fdowngraded from 24/7 cover to daytime
OL,19,Fhours from Monday to Friday.
