OL,7,FThe service's national plans follow
OL,8,Fthe need to spend more than #800m to
OL,9,Faddress a backlog of repairs in
OL,10,Fbuildings and equipment, insisting it
OL,11,Fwill not compromise public safety.
OL,13,FKevin and Diane White, from Hawick,
OL,14,Fwho experienced a home fire a few
OL,15,Fyears ago, say with the new plans it
OL,16,F"scares us to think if anything ever
OL,17,Fdid happen like that again".
OL,19,FKevin said: "Flames from the lounge
OL,20,Fwere hitting the bedroom window. It
OL,21,Fwas very, very scary.
