OL,7,F"It's still so fresh in your brains,
OL,8,Fyou know.... even with neighbours
OL,9,Faround us, what would happen in 20
OL,10,Fminutes to get down to us?
OL,12,F"It's the most ridiculous idea that
OL,13,FI've heard in a long time. I'm now
OL,14,Fdisabled, and my stomach is churning
OL,15,Fjust thinking about me being like this
OL,16,Fat the time of the fire."
