OL,3,CResidents say proposals to downgrade
OL,4,Cthe town's fire station could 'cost
OL,5,Clives'
OL,7,FDeputy Assistant Chief Officer Garry
OL,8,FMackay, from the Scottish Fire and
OL,9,FRescue Service, says he understands
OL,10,Fthe concerns about changing the
OL,11,Foperation of Hawick's fire service.
OL,13,FHe said: "I don't believe it comprises
OL,14,Fpublic safety - I want to be really
OL,15,Fstrong in that response. What I would
OL,16,Fsay is, what we are proposing is a
OL,17,Frange of changes that could impact the
OL,18,Flocation of fire stations, the way we
OL,19,Fcrew appliances and the way our duty
OL,20,Fpatterns operate across the country."
