OL,3,CResidents say proposals to downgrade
OL,4,Cthe town's fire station could 'cost
OL,5,Clives'
OL,7,FThe proposals involve more than 30
OL,8,Ffire stations across 14 different
OL,9,Flocal authorities, offering 23 options
OL,10,Ffor change.
OL,12,FGreg McLeod, from the Fire Brigade
OL,13,FUnion, said: "We've explicitly stated
OL,14,Fthat the downgrade of Hawick Fire
OL,15,FStation from the 24/7 cover to a day
OL,16,Fshift duty system with on-call in the
OL,17,Fevenings and weekends will potentially
OL,18,Fcost lives due to the slow response
OL,19,Ftimes."
