OL,5,Clives'
OL,7,FKaymire Hughes, also from Hawick,
OL,8,Fsaid: "I've put together a whole
OL,9,Fcampaign around delivering leaflets,
OL,10,Fgetting the word out, engaging with
OL,11,Fstakeholders, you know, making it
OL,12,Freally difficult for them to close the
OL,13,Ffire station during the weekends.
OL,15,F"I need people to help me go around
OL,16,Fthe local towns because it doesn't
OL,17,Fjust affect Hawick, it affects
OL,18,FSelkirk, Jedburgh and Newcastleton
OL,19,Ftoo."
