OL,4,Cthe town's fire station could 'cost
OL,5,Clives'
OL,7,FWill Roberts, from Cavers, says he
OL,8,F'could have lost his life' if
OL,9,Ffirefighters needed to travel further
OL,10,Faway from Hawick.
OL,12,FHe said: "End of November last year, I
OL,13,Ffound my garage alight, burning quite
OL,14,Fremarkably. I tried to put it out with
OL,15,Fa garden hose, clearly it wasn't going
OL,16,Fto (go out).
